{"tid":1333392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［廣傳］新物資，一人入一支水比前線","createTime":"2019-07-19T16:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T01:49:46.000Z","uid":32906,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"657114b94985b48c78e86d673454cb86420a9cb1","tid":1333392,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:18:34.000Z","msg":"一支水，係和理非提供到既最低成本物資<br />\n<br />\n唔一定要買，自己留個樽入滿水帶比集會人士<br />\n因為其他樽都比水樽硬身<br />\n<br />\n一人手拎一支有咩效果？<br />\n有煙蛋可以立刻撲救<br />\n<br />\n有狗口渴衝過黎？<br />\n果斷一支支咁請佢<br />\n唔好再幻想點樣打狗，你打佢十下<br />\n佢一下收你皮。<br />\n<br />\n仲講緊波子 防潮珠 油 報紙？<br />\n一地水樽就已經可以陰到佢地踩波車<br />\n<br />\n到時一定會有好多，點分配？留低既人最好一人咩一支<br />\n未開既新水留少少係物資站<br />\n開過既就全部拎比前線 再分前中後點堆放<br />\nhit and run<br />\n<br />\nQnA<br />\n其他罐裝飲品得唔得？<br />\n    你鍾意啦，唔阻止你<br />\n<br />\n飲過有你口水咪有dna？<br />\n    有又點？咪證明到支水你飲過囉，仲證明到d咩<br />\n    香港無dna 資料庫，唔可能咁樣就搵得番你<br />\n<br />\n咁有人入其他野咪好大獲<br />\n    飲自己帶果支或飲未開既水<br />\n<br />\n比狗查咁點算？<br />\n    水黎姐！呀sir<br />\n<br />\n點解係水樽<br />\n    因為看似最唔暴力，遠攻又易入門<br />\n<br />\n水樽都唔痛<br />\n<br />\n［科普知識］水樽比你想像中強大<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1318700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1318700</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n你睇完再講<br />\n<br />\n仲有咩下面再討論"},{"pid":"c2efb5270b9bc7811583aaf55e8441a3f3c71966","tid":1333392,"uid":32906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:30:49.000Z","msg":"一人一支係手改變被暴打命運"},{"pid":"2af6185c6cac59ecd8066a075096b6ab3684e75b","tid":1333392,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:17:04.000Z","msg":"埋黎睇下啦"},{"pid":"f53bae837611d0774bf1d7401aad7ecca6f4d060","tid":1333392,"uid":272010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:21:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />補充水分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"498883133c5ab8989c136168f3185b6b8ba3d166","tid":1333392,"uid":32906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:32:02.000Z","msg":"近攻幾時都係輸家"},{"pid":"e0f87c1349cd4ea5e1441ab710c938f30ef62610","tid":1333392,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:33:48.000Z","msg":"自己唔敢出手 就送比前線"},{"pid":"99fcb1192fc9afd518187f2be35ca8ec62a4456d","tid":1333392,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:47:37.000Z","msg":"遠攻 已經發展緊<br />\n因為資源太少未有真正效果<br />\n唔通一個人拎十幾支咩<br />\n<br />\n所以始終都係要靠大家"},{"pid":"94567f34e814a85b0021a4c31d372fc75d388f0c","tid":1333392,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:52:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a69f885434b8d0c91d268f8ebdb2ce673c7b4507","tid":1333392,"uid":265374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:04:30.000Z","msg":"天氣熱,羅多2支水"},{"pid":"29ed1fb367a4d680d758e4a60aaa573704645c10","tid":1333392,"uid":247690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:07:11.000Z","msg":"見過有D水樽好靚，底部特登加層金屬"},{"pid":"2705ca109772a1f5b842e50417119070ddabc05a","tid":1333392,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:13:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71ca8419e5969a5a16a7de287ea495dea2aaa52f","tid":1333392,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:31:06.000Z","msg":"點解唔飲玻璃樽裝可樂，好味過水咁多"},{"pid":"d32e78a83589589ef8a7f23f5f429c13adbb230e","tid":1333392,"uid":246884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:31:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f474ec0825119fe9d1e914513455f3d068299965","tid":1333392,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71ca8419e5969a5a16a7de287ea495dea2aaa52f","tid":1333392,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:31:06.000Z","msg":"點解唔飲玻璃樽裝可樂，好味過水咁多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T05:03:57.000Z","msg":"咪咁多ff啦"},{"pid":"8839a17b50cab128073d45329512c886db1e70fe","tid":1333392,"uid":32906,"like":0,"disli